Results.ReviewText: I never write reviews, however on this occasion it is warranted!  I bought these sachets of coffee expecting very little in all honesty,  but i couldnt have been more wrong!  The coffee packed a punch,  tasted smooth and smelled divine.  I thought it would be wishy washy,  lacking real coffeeness,  but i loved it.... As did all my colleagues.  Unfortunately!  I ended up having to get loads more whilst i could still find them!  Practical and scrummy!
Results.Title: So unexpected!

Results.ReviewText: Love these Nescafé sachets , they are small and compact ideal for putting in my backpack . I have an allotment and they are perfect to take as they are 3 in 1 no messing with milk and sugar . They also taste amazing when you want a great tasting drink .
Results.Title: Compact and easy

Results.ReviewText:
I buy every 2 weeks 20 pouch of Nescafe 3 in 1 smooth with 5 or 7 sachets inside and every day we have 3 to 4 cups of coffee, we cannot live without. 
As Italian we cannot live without coffee but we are drinking less expresso and more Nescafe 3 in 1
Results.Title: Love 3 in 1 smooth Nescafe coffee

Results.ReviewText: Bought this recently to use for my night fishing trips it's awesome, smooth and easy to use with a flask of hot water cracking stuff
Results.Title: Excellent for night trips
